"form.d.ts",
"geo.js",       // ← add
"geo.d.ts",     // ← add
"router.js",
```

---

### Step 5 — Test file: `geo.test.ts`

Create `packages/next/src/server/web/spec-extension/geo.test.ts` using Jest (the codebase standard — see `packages/next/src/lib/batcher.test.ts` and `spec-extension/adapters/headers.test.ts` for style):

